Prerequisites

Make sure you have python3, matplotlib and astropy installed on your
system. If you are using python 2 by default in your system then you
may need to install specifically the libraries specifically for
python3.

To install;

1) mkdir ~/.myPrograms (if it doesn't already exist)
2) cd ~/.myPrograms
3) ln -s route/directory/for/damfits.py damfits
4) Add the following line at the end of your .bashrc (or .zshrc ...):

             export PATH=$PATH:~/.myPrograms

